{"tid":1796984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屯公大媽發起「反暴力」集會　與大叔阿伯圍困區議員","createTime":"2019-12-25T04:50:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-25T06:13:04.000Z","uid":81228,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"999085717e716766a766f4d5c4eb5507abf4dc9b","tid":1796984,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T04:50:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/12/20191224_PO_%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%922-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F12%2F20191224_PO_%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%259C%25922-1.jpg&h=4cde715c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n候任區議員張錦雄重申，康文署應阻止大媽拖音響入園<br />\n<br />\n屯門公園上周六有多名候任區議員不滿大媽熱舞死灰復燃，促請康文署加強執法，最後沒收大媽的音響。今天有2名唱歌大媽發起「反暴力」集會，圍困3名當值候任議員，並舉起手機拍攝，其他候任區議員亦有到場解困，引來不少街坊圍觀。候任屯門區議員會張錦雄重申，康文署公園經理應該阻止大媽拖音響進入公園，如同阻止單車一樣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/12/20191224_PO_%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F12%2F20191224_PO_%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%259C%2592.jpg&h=2a26ece5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nFB「屯門開荒牛」圖片。<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/12/20191224_PO_%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%921.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F12%2F20191224_PO_%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%259C%25921.jpg&h=aafe5741&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nFB「屯門開荒牛」圖片。<br />\n<br />\n張錦雄又指，那些「表演集團」有備而來，指兩位大媽「喊咪」煽動大叔阿伯起哄，企圖以聲勢嚇走在場議員。張錦雄重申不會感到懼怕，因他們是民意授權去監督康文署執法，務求還公園安寧。只要公園繼續「烏煙瘴氣」，繼續存在嚴重嘈音，只要康文署和其他相關部門不作為，議員都會繼續輪流到屯門公園「值班」，直到問題得到圓滿解決為止。<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/12/20191224_PO_%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%922.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F12%2F20191224_PO_%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%259C%25922.jpg&h=247150a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nFB「屯門開荒牛」圖片。<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/12/191209_CR_%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%803.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F12%2F191209_CR_%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%25803.jpg&h=2e1dda37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「屯門三公主」早前已回歸屯門公園。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/5636603-2%e5%90%8d%e5%b1%af%e5%85%ac%e5%a4%a7%e5%aa%bd%e7%99%bc%e8%b5%b7%e3%80%8c%e5%8f%8d%e6%9a%b4%e5%8a%9b%e3%80%8d%e9%9b%86%e6%9c%83-%e5%8d%80%e8%ad%b0%e5%93%a1%e9%81%ad%e5%9c%8d%e5%9b%b0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F5636603-2%25e5%2590%258d%25e5%25b1%25af%25e5%2585%25ac%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e5%25aa%25bd%25e7%2599%25bc%25e8%25b5%25b7%25e3%2580%258c%25e5%258f%258d%25e6%259a%25b4%25e5%258a%259b%25e3%2580%258d%25e9%259b%2586%25e6%259c%2583-%25e5%258d%2580%25e8%25ad%25b0%25e5%2593%25a1%25e9%2581%25ad%25e5%259c%258d%25e5%259b%25b0&d=nB3K3ojK8rN8kNU4dsXAY09C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=14d48ff5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/5636603-2%e5%90%8d%e5%b1%af%e5%85%ac%e5%a4%a7%e5%aa%bd%e7%99%bc%e8%b5%b7%e3%80%8c%e5%8f%8d%e6%9a%b4%e5%8a%9b%e3%80%8d%e9%9b%86%e6%9c%83-%e5%8d%80%e8%ad%b0%e5%93%a1%e9%81%ad%e5%9c%8d%e5%9b%b0</a>"},{"pid":"2a89df738fc8300e2d3f2edb55b8fca778bcc0b5","tid":1796984,"uid":253016,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T04:51:55.000Z","msg":"反暴力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你班藍屍廢老支那豬就最暴力個堆黎"},{"pid":"288d88e60afd8d54921a27295bfcfa3802a5f783","tid":1796984,"uid":54927,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T04:55:02.000Z","msg":"老老實實火魔3公主其中一個以後都唔會再有呢啲問題發生"},{"pid":"1c1681f4509ea9bf7f47be4eabb50ff2c07eb80b","tid":1796984,"uid":103325,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T04:57:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聖誕節食火雞"},{"pid":"7de6fff97905d12245e5034ade7db17b196369ff","tid":1796984,"uid":240608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T04:57:29.000Z","msg":"鬥人多囉"},{"pid":"7e470b3d0b9132169f8a531ee0a6c3c7a22355cd","tid":1796984,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T05:00:05.000Z","msg":"屯門個tg好廢  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />變晒質"},{"pid":"370a22eb3108408ddf257da971703c55d84969dd","tid":1796984,"uid":328114,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T05:01:07.000Z","msg":"你一唱歌日日同你報黑警有冇得諗<br />\n<br />\n有人黑衣人聚集<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fdc331cb07b205e388b8a6148887a545d674bfb","tid":1796984,"uid":19126,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"288d88e60afd8d54921a27295bfcfa3802a5f783","tid":1796984,"uid":54927,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T04:55:02.000Z","msg":"老老實實火魔3公主其中一個以後都唔會再有呢啲問題發生"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T05:02:18.000Z","msg":"三個好似成日企埋一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45675282f37358ec2945f67c7b6ad24c731bbfc1","tid":1796984,"uid":43953,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3fdc331cb07b205e388b8a6148887a545d674bfb","tid":1796984,"uid":19126,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"288d88e60afd8d54921a27295bfcfa3802a5f783","tid":1796984,"uid":54927,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T04:55:02.000Z","msg":"老老實實火魔3公主其中一個以後都唔會再有呢啲問題發生"},"citedBy":1,"r